              ],
              "free_text": [
                " The detector is a plastic scintillator (NE",
                "101), 1 cm in diameter 1 cm high, mounted directly on",
                "the face of the photomultiplier tube Du Mont 6292. A",
                "ring geometry is used for scattering, in which the",
                "angle of scattering is varied both by using different",
                "size rings and by a movement of each ring along the",
                "source-detector axis. In this way, an angular range",
                "from 10 to 138 degree is covered."
              ]
